OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782134326
OL,3,CBristol city centre evacuated after
OL,4,Cgas main ruptures
OL,6,FResidents are being evacuated from
OL,7,Fhomes and buildings as emergency
OL,8,Fservices respond to a ruptured gas
OL,9,Fmain.
OL,11,FAvon Fire and Rescue is currently
OL,12,Fresponding to a gas leak on Colston
OL,13,FStreet in the centre of Bristol.
OL,15,FAuthorities have set up a 200m cordon
OL,16,Fincluding the St James Barton
OL,17,FRoundabout through to Park Row, Park
OL,18,FStreet, and Anchor Road in Bristol.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
