OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782134326
OL,3,CBristol city centre evacuated after
OL,4,Cgas main ruptures
OL,6,FAvon Fire and Rescue Service has urged
OL,7,Fthe public to avoid these areas to
OL,8,Fprevent further congestion due to the
OL,9,Flarge number of emergency response
OL,10,Fvehicles at the scene.
OL,12,FAmbulance crews and Wales & West
OL,13,FUtilities are also in attendance, and
OL,14,Fare "actively monitoring the gas leak
OL,15,Fand working to isolate this as quickly
OL,16,Fas possible".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
