CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782134326
OL,3,CBristol city centre evacuated after
OL,4,Cgas main ruptures
OL,6,FThe Park Street closure means buses
OL,7,Fare being diverted via Anchor Road and
OL,8,FJacob Wells Road, meaning no services
OL,9,Fwill run to College Green or the top
OL,10,Fof Park Street.
OL,12,FIn a statement posted on social media,
OL,13,Fthe Bristol Beacon said that it had
OL,14,Fevacuated everyone inside as a
OL,15,F"precaution due to a damaged gas main
OL,16,Fnear to the venue."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
