OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782134326
OL,3,CBristol city centre evacuated after
OL,4,Cgas main ruptures
OL,6,FThey went onto say, "We are following
OL,7,Finstructions from the relevant
OL,8,Fauthorities and will update later this
OL,9,Fafternoon as to whether tonight's
OL,10,Fperformances with Arooj Aftab & London
OL,11,FContemporary Orchestra in Beacon Hall
OL,12,Fand Michel Padron's Afro Cuban
OL,13,FOrchestra in Lantern Hall can go
OL,14,Fahead."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
